title: Sri Lanka seeks way forward after president quits - BBC News
description: Sri Lanka is seeking a way out of political and economic chaos after its President Gotabaya Rajapaksa resigned and fled the country and Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe was appointed temporary leader. |After being sworn in as interim leader, Mr Wickremesinghe promised to act quickly to put a democratically elected president in place.|Given the governing party has a majority, MPs are thought likely to back Mr Wickremesinghe, who has close links with the Rajapaksa family.|But whether Sri Lanka's public would accept this is another matter, because Mr Wickremesinghe's resignation as PM was a key demand of protesters.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#SriLanka #BBCNews

title: Modi Govt to allow private players to develop military choppers; IMRH project first big test
description: In a big boost for self-reliance in defence, the Modi govt has allowed private players to develop Indian multi-role helicopters. title: 4 Poin Akan Dibongkar Komnas HAM Terkait Tewasnya Brigadir J
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Kapolri telah membentuk tim khusus untuk mengungkap kasus meninggalnya Brigadir J di rumah Irjen Ferdi Sambo pada Jumat 8 Juli lalu. ||||Sejumlah kejanggalan tercium oleh publik, atas kronologi versi polisi terkait kematian Brigadir J. ||||Brigadir J yang merupakan sopir dari istri Ferdi Sambo, diduga melecehkan Putri Chandrawati.||||Komisi Nasional Hak Asasi Manusia berjanji akan memeriksa CCTV di sekitar lokasi meskipun CCTV pertama sudah sempat diganti. ||||Baca Juga Komnas HAM Bakal Selidiki CCTV di Rumah Ferdy Sambo: Kami Punya Banyak Pengalaman Soal CCTV! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/309594/komnas-ham-bakal-selidiki-cctv-di-rumah-ferdy-sambo-kami-punya-banyak-pengalaman-soal-cctv||||Terkait luka sayatan di tubuh Brigadir J juga menjadi salah satu kejanggalan yang disebut publik. ||||"Tim kami yang ada divisi saya pemantauan dan penyelidikan melihat karakter pola. Yang kedua relasi luka misalnya apakah ini tembakan, sayatan, dan sebagainya," ucap Komisioner Komnas HAM Choirul Anam.||||Selain luka sayatan, Komnas HAM juga akan menelisik terkait luka tembakan pada tubuh Brigadir J, hingga mengunggkap motif dari penembakan itu. ||||Video Editor: Lintang|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/309987/4-poin-akan-dibongkar-komnas-ham-terkait-tewasnya-brigadir-j

title: Biden in a soup for fist-bump with Saudi Crown Prince; 'Human rights sold for oil' claim activists
description: US President Joe Biden's long cultivated image of a human rights' defender has been 'dented'. Biden faces the fury of rights activists and several Americans over fist-bump with Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed Bin Salman. Kenneth Roth, the executive director of Human Rights Watch shared the image on twitter and captioned it 'The autocrats of the world are smiling.' He further added that ''Biden's support for human rights can be sold for a smidgen of oil.' Many others have shared a Washington post article to slam the US President. In 2019, Biden vowed to make Saudi Arabia "pariah" over its human rights records. title: Beredar Pengakuan Kuasa Hukum Brigadir J Tunjukkan Bukti Foto Bukan karena Tembakan, Ini Kata Polisi
description: TRIBUN-VIDEO.COM - Dugaan adanya ketidakwajaran kondisi luka di tubuh Brigadir Yosua Hutabarat atau Brigadir J menjadi sorotan banyak pihak.|Berbagai video soal kondisi tak wajar dan janggal itupun akhirnya ditanggapi kepolisian.|Kepolisian mengungkapkan bahwa Brigadir J tewas seusai terlibat baku tembak dengan Bharada E.|Insiden itu terjadi di kediaman Kadiv Propam Polri Irjen Ferdy Sambo di kompleks Polri Jumat (8/7/2022) lalu.|Terkait banyaknya dugaan soal kondisi luka di tubuh Brigadir J yang tak wajar, Kadiv Humas Polri Irjen Dedi Prasetyo meminta agar publik bersabar.|Pasalnya, tim khusus yang dibentuk Kapolri Jenderal Listyo Sigit saat ini masih bekerja.|"Biar tim selesai bekerja dulu," ujar Dedi saat dimintai konfirmasi Kompas.com, Minggu (17/7/2022).|Ia pun berjanji bahwa segala informasi soal kasus tewasnya Brigadir J akan diungkap apabila hasilnya sudah ditemukan.|Dedi mengatakan, hasil yang akan diberikan tim khusus itu merupakan pembuktian secara ilmiah. |"Bukan asumsi-asumsi yang dikembangkan orang-orang bukan kompetensinya," ucapnya.|Sementara itu, Kabag Penum Divisi Humas Polri Kombes Nurul Azizah meminta publik bersabar menunggu hasil dari tim khusus mengenai dugaan penyiksaan tersebut.|"Tunggu hasil tim khusus ya. Mohon sabar," kata Nurul dikonfirmasi terpisah.|Meski begitu, Kombes Nurul Azizah tak membeberkan|Dalam video yang viral, seorang pria yang merupakan pengacara Komaruddin Simanjuntak menunjukkan beberapa foto soal kondisi luka dari Brigadir J.|Dilaporkan, bahwas Komaruddin ditunjuk oleh keluarga Brigadir J untuk menjadi kuasa hukum.|Dalam foto yang ditunjukkan itu, terlihat bagaimana beberapa luka tak wajar di tubuh Brigadir J dan bukan berasal dari luka tembakan.|Komaruddin menyebut bahwa apabila Brigadir J tewas karena luka tembak, maka tak mungkin ada luka yang tampak seperti sayatan atau tusukan.|Menurutnya, luka di tubuh Brigadir J itu diduga ditimbulkan oleh pedang atau pisau sangkur.|Terlebih, dalam foto-foto yang ditampilkan, pria itu mempertanyakan banyaknya bekas jahitan di tubuh Brigadir J.|Sebelumnya, kepolisian memastikan bahwa luka seperti sayatan di tubuh Brigadir J bukan karena senjata tajam.|Karo Penmas Divisi Humas Polri Brigjen Pol Ahmad Ramadan mengungkapkan bahwa luka sayatan itu berasal dari gesekan proyektil peluru yang dikeluarkan oleh Bharada E.|"Bukan (luka sayatan senjata tajam)."|"Kita bukan lihat tapi penjelasan penyidik soal sayatan adalah karena gesekan proyektil yang ditembakan oleh Bharada E ke Beigadir J," jelasnya.|(Tribun-Video.com)|Artikel ini telah tayang di Kompas.com dengan judul "Viral Video Penjelasan Luka Tak Wajar di Tubuh Brigadir J, Ini Tanggapan Polri", |https://nasional.kompas.com/read/2022/07/17/11130701/viral-video-penjelasan-luka-tak-wajar-di-tubuh-brigadir-j-ini-tanggapan?|Editor Video: Fatkhul Putra|Host: Nila Irda|#BrigadirJ|#KadivPropam|#KuasaHukum

title: Presiden Jokowi Menerima Direktur Pelaksana IMF, Istana Bogor, 17 Juli 2022
description: *Presiden Jokowi Terima Delegasi Dana Moneter Internasional*|Presiden Joko Widodo menerima delegasi Dana Moneter Internasional (IMF) di Istana Kepresidenan Bogor, Jawa Barat, Minggu, 17 Juli 2022. Delegasi yang hadir yaitu Direktur Pelaksana IMF Kristalina Georgieva, Direktur Departemen Asia dan Pasifik IMF Krishna Srinivasan, dan Representatif Senior IMF untuk Indonesia James Walsh. |Saat memberikan keterangan seusai mendampingi Presiden Jokowi, Menteri Koordinator Bidang Perekonomian (Menko Perekonomian) Airlangga Hartarto mengatakan bahwa dalam pertemuan tersebut Presiden Jokowi menyampaikan sejumlah hal kepada IMF mengenai situasi perekonomian di Indonesia. |"Ekonomi Indonesia relatif sedang baik di mana inflasi sekitar 4,2 persen, pertumbuhan 5,01 persen. Kemudian juga dalam situasi lain Indonesia, ekonomi dibanding negara lain kita punya _debt to GDP ratio_ sekitar 42 persen, beberapa negara itu mencapai 100 persen. Kemudian defisit masih sekitar 4 persen dan _current account_ 0,5 persen dan _balance of trade_ kita 26 bulan positif terus, dan Indonesia punya _foreign reserve_ sebesar USD135 miliar," ujar Menko Perekonomian.|Airlangga menjelaskan bahwa situasi perekonomian di Indonesia relatif baik dengan potensi resesi lebih kecil jika dibandingkan negara lain yaitu sekitar 3 persen. Meski demikian, pemerintah berharap IMF akan terus mendukung dan memberikan narasi positif terhadap perekonomian Indonesia terutama dalam menghadapi krisis global.|"Kita sangat mengkhawatirkan dengan kondisi inflasi yang naik di berbagai negara. Tingkat suku bunga akan masuk rezim baru yaitu kenaikan tingkat suku bunga global dan tentu sangat mempengaruhi terhadap investasi yang sangat dibutuhkan oleh Indonesia," lanjutnya. |Dalam keterangan yang sama, Menteri Keuangan (Menkeu) Sri Mulyani menyampaikan bahwa IMF menilai perekonomian Indonesia dalam kondisi baik dari beberapa sisi seperti kinerja ekonomi, sisi pertumbuhan, sisi neraca pembayaran yang mengalami surplus perdagangan selama 26 bulan berturut-turut, dan sisi inflasi yang berada di bawah 5 persen. |"Paling penting yaitu sinkronisasi dan kerja sama kebijakan moneter fiskal dari Bank Indonesia dan Kementerian Keuangan untuk bisa menjaga untuk tetap bekerja secara harmonis karena ini akan membantu menjaga momentum pemulihan ekonomi Indonesia," ucap Sri Mulyani. |Selain itu, Menkeu menyebut bahwa dalam pertemuan tersebut Direktur Pelaksana IMF, Kristalina juga menyampaikan apresiasi kepada pemerintah Indonesia atas penanganan pandemi Covid-19. |"Selanjutnya kita tentu berharap kondisi Indonesia yang membaik ini tetap dijaga karena nanti Bapak Presiden akan menjadi tuan rumah (KTT G20) pada bulan November," tandasnya.|Bogor, 17 Juli 2022|Biro Pers, Media, dan Informasi Sekretariat Presiden|Website: https://www.presidenri.go.id|YouTube: Sekretariat Presiden

title: Ini Sejumlah Luka di Tubuh Brigadir J, Hasil Autopsi Dipertanyakan: Setelah atau Sebelum Ditembak?
description: TRIBUN-VIDEO.COM - Kuasa hukum keluarga mendiang Brigadir Nofriansyah Yosua Hutabarat, Kamarrudin Simanjuntak mempertanyakan hasil autopsi dari Polri.|Pihaknya sangsi, setelah mengungkap luka-luka yang dialami Brigadir Yosua.|Dalam keterangannya pada Sabtu (16/7/2022), ia mengungkap ke publik sejumlah luka janggal yang ada pada tubuh Brigadir Yosua.|Kamaruddin mengatakan, ada beberapa bagian tubuh Brigadir J terdapat bekas pukulan hingga jahitan.|Kemudian di bawah tangannya ada luka robek diduga akibat benda tajam yang mengenai bagian bawah tangannya.|Selanjutnya, kejanggalan lainnya ada pada bagian kaki korban mengalami luka robek seperti di bawah tangan.|Padahal kalau tewas mengenakan seragam dinas, korban memakai kaos kaki.|Luka lainnya pada tubuh Yosua misalnya di bawah telinga ada luka robek sekira 10 centimeter|Selain itu, lubang telinga mengalami bengkak dan juga rahangnya bergeser.|Namun, ia belum mengetahui apakah itu karena senjata tajam atau pukulan.|Tapi ada pula dugaan luka tembakan yang menyerempet ke bagian bawah ketiak.|Terakhir, luka di jari yang sampai tak bisa berfungsi lagi alias syarafnya telah terputus.|Kamaruddin pun mempertanyakan hasil autopsi yang dilakukan oleh polisi sebelumnya.|Lantaran, sampai saat ini tidak disebutkan apakah luka itu terjadi setelah ditembak atau sebelum ditembak yang seharusnya sudah terungkap saat autopsi.(*)|VP : Sigit Setiawan|Host : Dea Mita

title: Wakapolri Jawab Tegas Soal Pengganti Kadiv Propam Irjen Ferdi Sambo
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Kasus penembakan Brigadir J oleh Bharada E di rumah Kadiv propam Irjen Ferdi Sambo, jadi perhatian publik. ||||Isu pencopotan Irjen Ferdy Sambo pun turut mencuat di berbagai media. ||||Atas isu ini, Wakapolri, Komjen Gatot Eddy angkat bicara. ||||"Kita semua dalam proses, jadi saya minta teman-teman menunggu saja, yang dilakukan oleh penyidik untuk mengambil keterangan-keterangan saksi-saksi yang ada," kata Gatot kepada wartawan di kantor Komisi Nasional Hak Asasi Manusia (Komnas HAM), Jumat (15/7/2022).||||Baca Juga Jurnalis Diintimidasi Saat Liput Rumah Irjen Ferdi Sambo, Polisi Minta Maaf di https://www.kompas.tv/article/309522/jurnalis-diintimidasi-saat-liput-rumah-irjen-ferdi-sambo-polisi-minta-maaf||||Kini mata publik tertuju pada pengungkapan fakta-fakta di lapangan oleh kepolisian dan tim yang dibentuk. ||||Dalam konferensi pers yang disampaikan Karo Penmas Brigjen Pol Ahmad Ramadhan mengungkap penembakan Brigadir J dimulai ketika teriakan istri Irjen Ferdi Sambo meminta tolong. ||||Brigadir J diduga melecehkan istri Irjen Ferdi Sambo dan kemudian ditembak Bharada E yang merupakan penjaga keamanan di rumah itu. ||||Video Editor: Lintang|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/309948/wakapolri-jawab-tegas-soal-pengganti-kadiv-propam-irjen-ferdi-sambo

title: Morissette - Power (from Miss Universe Philippines, the FIRST TAKE from our recording session)
description: not a lot of people know that when I performed this at the MOA Arena for The Coronation of 2022 Miss Universe Philippines, we didn't have our session in the studio yet since I literally had just come from the U.S for our recent tour. standard practice would be we'd record a song to also somewhat master the track first before even performing it live, but this was an exemption. it also took us a while after then to finally get back into the studio due to the somewhat return of "normalcy" nowadays and getting ourselves loaded with work. |we initially already had a date to record this track with my Kuya Kikx, but I was feeling under the weather and caught the flu which also affected my voice so we had to postpone. weeks passed and on this day, I was in the studio with Dave working on some stuff when I randomly said, "we should try to record 'Power' again." mind you, we had other plans that evening but this was just a "spur of the moment" kind of thing. perks of having our own studio, he opens the session and this right here was our very first take. of course we did several more after that and finished in just around 20 minutes. I decided to shoot with my phone just for memories sake, but this turned out better than we thought.. and just wanted to share this with all of you ‚ô°|*PLEASE NOTE THAT THE OFFICIAL VERSION IS DIFFERENT FROM WHAT'S HEARD ON THIS VIDEO. this is just one take out of many we did that night, comped mixed and mastered for the best to be put out there. enjoy!|-------------------------|POWER (from Miss Universe Philippines 'Coronation')|by Morissette|written by Kiko Salazar|label: Empire Ph|*special thanks to Sir Jonas Gaffud for the opportunity!|check out https://amap.to/morissette/ for more and other info!|#Morissette

title: Kardea Brown's Fancy BLTs ‚Äã| Delicious Miss Brown | Food Network
description: Kardea amps up the flavor of her BLTs with tangy pickled green tomatoes and a homemade garlic aioli!|Watch #DeliciousMissBrown, Sundays at 12|11c + subscribe to #discoveryplus to stream the entire library and so much more: http://discoverypl.us/2NeKVgd. |Get the recipe ‚ñ∂ https://foodtv.com/3IBZK56|Subscribe to Food Network ‚ñ∂ http://foodtv.com/YouTube|Kardea Brown shares down-home, Southern recipes from her South Carolina kitchen. The cook and caterer was born and raised on the sea islands of Charleston, the heart of all Southern cooking, and learned to cook in her grandmother's kitchen. These days, she takes generations of family recipes and makes them her own as she cooks for family and friends at her Sea Island home.|Welcome to Food Network, where learning to cook is as simple as clicking play! Grab your apron and get ready to get cookin' with some of the best chefs around the world. We'll give you a behind-the-scenes look at our best shows, take you inside our favorite restaurant and be your resource in the kitchen to make sure every meal is a 10/10!|Fancy BLTs with Pickled Tomatoes|RECIPE COURTESY OF KARDEA BROWN|Level: Easy|Total: 2 hr 5 min (includes cooling time)|Active: 35 min|Yield: 4 sandwiches|Ingredients|Pickled Green Tomatoes:|2 to 3 large green tomatoes, sliced|1 tablespoon pickling spice|1 cup red wine vinegar (or vinegar of your choice)|1 tablespoon sugar|Kosher salt|Roasted Garlic Aioli:|1 head garlic|1 tablespoon olive oil|1 large pasteurized egg yolk, at room temperature (no more than 2 hours)|1 tablespoon Dijon mustard|1 tablespoon fresh lemon juice|1 cup vegetable or canola oil|Kosher salt and freshly ground pepper|Sandwiches:|8 slices thick-cut artisan bread (or your favorite bread), toasted|16 slices applewood-smoked thick-cut bacon|8 leaves iceberg or butter lettuce|Kosher salt and freshly ground black pepper|Directions|Special equipment: a 32-ounce mason jar|Make the pickled tomatoes: Pack the tomatoes into a 32-ounce mason jar. Add the pickling spice. Heat the vinegar, sugar, 1 tablespoon salt and 1 cup water in a medium saucepan over medium heat, stirring, until the sugar and salt dissolve, about 1 minute. Let cool about 5 minutes, then pour over the tomatoes. Let cool to room temperature for at least 1 hour, then refrigerate until ready to use.|Make the roasted garlic aioli: Preheat the oven to 400 degrees F.|Cut 1/4 to 1/2 inch from the top of the head of garlic, keeping the bulb intact. Place on a sheet of aluminum foil and drizzle with the olive oil. Wrap tightly with foil. Bake until the cloves are golden and soft when pressed, 30 to 40 minutes. Squeeze the cloves into a small bowl. Let cool completely, about 30 minutes.|Meanwhile, whisk the egg yolk in a medium bowl then whisk in the mustard until combined. Gradually whisk in the lemon juice until frothy. Slowly add the vegetable oil in a thin stream, whisking vigorously, until the mixture thickens. Whisk in the cooled garlic and season with salt and pepper.|Assemble the sandwiches: Cook the bacon in a large skillet over medium-high heat, turning occasionally, until browned and crisp, about 8 to 10 minutes. Remove to paper towels to drain. Spread the roasted garlic aioli on one side of the toasted bread slices. Top 4 slices of the bread with the bacon. Top with the lettuce and pickled tomatoes and sprinkle with salt and pepper. Top with the remaining bread slices and cut in half.|Cook‚Äôs Note|Use pasteurized egg yolk for food safety.|Subscribe to our channel to fill up on the latest must-eat recipes, brilliant kitchen hacks and content from your favorite Food Network shows.|‚ñ∂ FOOD NETWORK KITCHEN APP: http://foodtv.com/FNKApp|‚ñ∂ WEBSITE: https://www.foodnetwork.com|‚ñ∂ FULL EPISODES: https://watch.foodnetwork.com|‚ñ∂ FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/FoodNetwork|‚ñ∂ INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/FoodNetwork|‚ñ∂ TWITTER: https://twitter.com/FoodNetwork|#KardeaBrown #DeliciousMissBrown #FoodNetwork #FancyBLTs|Kardea Brown's Fancy BLTs ‚Äã| Delicious Miss Brown | Food Network|https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fiwti9T9Bew

title: How to get ARRESTED at an MLB game -- DON'T do this or else
description: Phillies fans are a special kind of crazy, and it wasn't just the idiot who ran on the field. Make sure to watch this until the VERY end for some bonus shenanigans. Citizens Bank Park -- what a place to watch a baseball game. |The St. Louis Cardinals were in Philly, and Paul Goldschmidt was going for his 300th career home run. That's the main reason that I made the trip, but I had a great time hanging with my friend Ben Weil (@benny_bang_bang on Instagram), my intern Max Edelman (@max_edelman), and video editor Zac Gutherman (@zg_films). As I mentioned in the video, this was the first time that Zac and I met in person, so this was his first time filming for me. Sold-out game over the July 4th weekend? Hell, why not! And it all worked out. And just for the record,  this took place on July 3, 2022. |Thanks for watching!

title: Incredible Rory McIlroy bunker shot sets up Sunday battle | Round 3 Full Highlights
description: Rory McIlroy and Viktor Hovland will enter the final day of The 150th Open tied at the top of the leaderboard after going toe-to-toe across a sensational Saturday at St Andrews.|The pair each recorded superb 66s to take themselves to 16-under-par, four shots clear of Cameron Smith and Cameron Young, and lay the foundations for a final-day shootout reminiscent of the Duel in the Sun in 1977.|The European duo went out as the penultimate group but were soon setting the pace, Hovland recording four consecutive birdies between holes 3 and 6 to leapfrog overnight leader Smith.|McIlroy joined him in a share of the lead with a sublime chip-in for eagle from a bunker at the 10th and there was nothing to separate the two by the 18th green, on which both converted birdie putts to leave the final round tantalisingly poised.|Smith was unable to build on his day two momentum, a bogey on the 1st followed by an unwanted tour of the rough en route to a double bogey at 13 to leave the Australian playing catch-up but very much still in the hunt.|Visit www.TheOpen.com for the greatest stories in golf|Keep in touch with us!|Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/The-Open-Championship/ |Twitter - https://twitter.com/TheOpen |Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/theopen/|To LICENSE The Open footage, please contact IMG REPLAY   ‚ñ∂ https://bit.ly/306V7dI

description: Ivana Trump's cause of death has been revealed. A senior New York City official told NBC News that the circumstances of Trump's death are consistent with a fall on the stairs in her Manhattan home. There is no foul play suspected.

description: Ukraine has said that Russia is using its Zaporizhzhia nuclear plant as a base to store weapons. Russian Defence Minister Sergei Shoigu has ordered his military units operating in Ukraine to step up their operations. title: HIMARS Strikes Russia Hard In Ukraine War | Why Taiwan Wants The Same Advantage Against Xi's China
description: The powerful US-made missile system HIMARS has been praised for shifting the balance of war in Ukraine with its effectiveness. Russia has already confirmed that Ukraine has attacked its occupied territories with the US-made HIMARS. Taiwan, which faces Chinese incursions on a regular basis, has announced the purchase of two more HIMARS. In June, Taiwan signed two arms deals worth $1.75 billion with the US, in what could fuel further tensions with China. The deal involves Taiwan getting two more HIMARS and anti-ship Harpoon missiles from the US. title: Why Jasmine Oil Is So Expensive | So Expensive | Business Insider
description: A kilogram of jasmine oil can cost $5,000. But to get that small amount of oil, harvesters need to handpick over 5,000 jasmine buds. Once the flower blooms, producers in India quickly process it into one of the priciest absolute oils in the world. title: Building a Lego-powered Submarine 4.0 - automatic depth control
description: This radio-controlled submarine can maintain a steady depth or a certain distance from the bottom. It is equipped with a pressure sensor and a laser distance sensor. Raspberry Pi and PID control are used for automation. Tested in a swimming pool and a small river (at the end of the video). Enjoy!|0:00 building|2:36 tests in water|3:48 long journey in a small river|6:47 full Python code|SPECS|Displacement: 2.4 kg (5.3 lb)|Test depth: 1.5 m (5 ft)|Hull: acrylic plastic cylinder (250x110x3mm), SAN plastic lid (2mm thick)|Lid seal: o-ring 2.5 mm (NBR 70 shore)|Ballast tank: 60 ml syringe (Eotia marinade injector), Lego EV3 Medium Servo motor (45503)|Forward propeller: drone propeller (Diatone Bull Nose 4x4.5), Lego PF L-motor (88003)|Turn propeller: Lego propeller 3 blade (6041), Lego PF M-motor (8883)|Magnetic couplings: K&J Magnetics D38-N52 neodymium magnet, TapeCase 423-5 UHMW Tape, silicon spray|Motor driver: 2x Pololu 2130 DRV8833 Dual H-bridge|Radio control: 27 MHz controller dissembled from a toy submarine (no-name chinese Mini U Boat)|Pressure sensor: Honeywell SSCMANV030PA2A3 2 bar|Laser distance sensor: SparkFun TFMini-S Micro|Computer: Raspberry Pi Zero 2 W|Power supply: Lego Rechargeable Battery Box 9V (8878), Pololu 2123 S7V8F5 5V voltage regulator|On-board camera: RunCam 5 Orange|MORE DETAILS|https://brickexperimentchannel.wordpress.com/rc-submarine-4-0-blog-post-series/|LONG JOURNEY FULL VIDEO|https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rO5zHXUckKQ|CODE|https://mega.nz/folder/wqhhxJoI#cHnVI6NjaPkfZcdZvFZZ0Q|or|https://www.dropbox.com/sh/u8a45maz3brrwrw/AADbUx9VZEw5UJPny1bJI-Lwa|PREVIOUS SUBS|1.0 syringe ballast https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tGEZApd9MMk|2.0 magnetic couplings https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MdfUSNzc0Xk|3.0 balloon and compressor https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n83cSg3wohU|MUSIC|Tommy Baynen - Stone Paths|https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zepP1zdiUPI|https://colorize.ffm.to/0364|https://soundcloud.com/tommybaynen

title: Hands-On with Mojo Augmented Reality Contact Lens!
description: We go eyes-on with the feature prototype of Mojo Lens, an in-development contact lens with an embedded augmented reality display and the electronics needed to run it wirelessly. With a tethered prototype held up to our eye, we could clearly see how the .5mm wide microLED shows images and text as well as a user interface that can be controlled with literal eye tracking. title: Ukraine says Russia is storing weapons at Europe's biggest nuclear plant | DW News
description: Ukraine's nuclear agency says Russia is using a captured nuclear power plant to store weapons and attack targets. title: Biden holds no sway? Mohammed Bin Salman smirks & ignores question on Khashoggi murder | Watch

title: Why Summer Means Big Bucks For Companies | CNBC Marathon
description: CNBC Marathon explores how companies are cashing in on summer.|Over the last several decades, a growing number of Americans have chosen to spend more time and money on swimming pools. Many Americans are moving to the suburbs, migrating to warmer states and increasingly looking to make their own yards better places to spend time. Most pools can be found in California, Texas and Florida, but population growth in other Southern states is escalating the demand for pool construction and supplies. Pool Corporation, one of the largest pool supply distributers, has seen its stock price soar. Retailers and distributors such as Leslie‚Äôs and Pool Corp. are aiming to conquer the large and growing pool supply market, which offers pretty steady revenues from consumers trying to keep their pool water from turning green.|The outdoor deck is another summer staple. During the Covid-19 pandemic, Americans stuck at home started to take a hard look at their surroundings, leading to a home improvement boom. Skyrocketing demand and historically high lumber prices bear excellent fortune for a couple of publicly traded companies that make a rather humble-sounding product ‚Äì fake wood decks. Two of the biggest names in this space are Trex and AZEK. Together they control 75 percent of the composite decking market.|In addition to pools and decks, about a third of Americans spend at least some time on a boat. In the landscape of recreational power sports, which includes boats, some categories have seen their fair share of struggles in recent years. But boat industry revenues have been mostly growing. Boat sales have seen a boost during Covid, but some analysts think the growth is poised to continue.|CNBC Marathon brings together the best of CNBC on YouTube.|Chapters:|00:00 Introduction|00:39 Who Makes Money From America‚Äôs Pool Obsession (Published July 2021)|16:14 Why The Fake Wood Decking Business Is Booming (Published August 2021)|30:13 Why U.S. Boat Sales Are Booming (Published July 2021)|¬ª Subscribe to CNBC: https://cnb.cx/SubscribeCNBC|¬ª Subscribe to CNBC TV: https://cnb.cx/SubscribeCNBCtelevision|About CNBC: From 'Wall Street' to 'Main Street' to award winning original documentaries and Reality TV series, CNBC has you covered. title: The Handmaid's Tale - What's Come True and What Hasn't (Yet)

title: State-of-the-art Bundelkhand Expressway to give major boost to connectivity & development in UP
description: Prime Minister Narendra Modi visited Uttar Pradesh on 16th July, 2022 and inaugurated Bundelkhand Expressway at Kaitheri village in Orai tehsil of Jalaun district.|The government has been committed to enhancing connectivity across the country, a key feature of which has been the work towards improvement in road infrastructure. A significant endeavour towards this was the laying of foundation stone for the construction of Bundelkhand Expressway by the Prime Minister on 29 February, 2020. The work on the Expressway has been completed within 28 months and it will now be inaugurated by the Prime Minister.|The 296 Km, four-lane expressway has been constructed at a cost of around Rs 14,850 crores, under the aegis of Uttar Pradesh Expressways Industrial Development Authority (UPEIDA), and can later be expanded upto six lanes as well. It extends from NH-35 at Gonda village near Bharatkoop in Chitrakoot district to near Kudrail village in Etawah district, where it merges with the Agra-Lucknow expressway. It passes through seven districts, viz. Chitrakoot, Banda, Mahoba, Hamirpur, Jalaun, Auraiya and Etawah.|Along with improving connectivity in the region, the Bundelkhand Expressway will also give a major boost to economic development, resulting in the creation of thousands of jobs for the local people. Work on the creation of industrial corridor in Banda and Jalaun districts, next to the Expressway, has already been started.|Subscribe Now: https://goo.gl/8qsb5E Stay Updated! üîî||||Follow us to stay updated:||||‚ñ∫ Download the NM App: http://nm4.in/dnldapp||‚ñ∫ Like us on Facebook: https://facebook.com/narendramodi||‚ñ∫ Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/narendramodi||‚ñ∫ Follow us on Instagram: http://instagram.com/narendramodi

title: G20 Bahas Krisis Pangan & Energi Dunia, Sri Mulyani : Akhir 2022 Harga Pangan Bisa Naik 20 Persen!
description: NUSA DUA BALI, KOMPAS.TV - Menteri Keuangan dan Gubernur Bank Sentral negara-negara G20, hari ini melanjutkan rangkaian pertemuan pada jalur keuangan di Nusa Dua, Bali.||||Salah yang menjadi bahasan krusial adalah soal krisis pangan dunia, yang diprediksi bakal makin parah menjelang akhir 2022.||||Kondisi ekonomi dunia, yang masih belum sepenuhnya pulih akibat pandemi, semakin diperparah dengan invasi Rusia ke Ukraina.||||Baca Juga Bahas Krisis Ekonomi Sri Lanka di G20, Sri Mulyani Pastikan Ekonomi Domestik Cenderung Stabil di https://www.kompas.tv/article/309112/bahas-krisis-ekonomi-sri-lanka-di-g20-sri-mulyani-pastikan-ekonomi-domestik-cenderung-stabil||||Selain krisis energi, dunia juga dihadapkan pada krisis pangan terutama bagi negara-negara dengan ekonomi rentan.||||Dalam seminar di pertemuan G20 jalur keuangan, Nusa Dua Bali, Menteri Keuangan Sri Mulyani menyebut per bulan Maret, harga pangan sudah melonjak hampir 13 persen.||||Dan bisa melonjak hingga 20 persen pada akhir tahun 2022.||||Forum G20 diharapkan bisa menjadi jembatan solusi, dari hasil diskusi bersama para menteri keuangan dan gubernur bank sentral berbagai negara anggota.|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/309766/g20-bahas-krisis-pangan-energi-dunia-sri-mulyani-akhir-2022-harga-pangan-bisa-naik-20-persen

title: Isi Chat Terakhir Brigadir J di Grup Whatsapp Keluarga, Kenang Tempat Bermain Sewaktu Kecil
description: TRIBUN-VIDEO.COM - Brigadir J yang menjadi korban penembakan di rumah dinas Kadiv Propam Irjen Ferdy Sambo dikenal aktif memberi kabar di grup Whatsapp keluarga. |WA Brigadir J terakhir kalo aktif pada Jumat (8/7/2022) pukul 17.05 WIB. |Dalam percakapan terakhir di grup Whatsapp keluarga, Brigadir J mengenang lokasi bermainnya sewaktu kecil. |Pada (2/7/2022) pukul 14.46 WIB, Brigadir J memberikan kabar soal keberangkatannya ke Magelang, Jawa Tengah. |Ia juga menceritakan akan mengawal Kadiv Propam, Irjen Pol Ferdy Sambo beserta istri dan anaknya. |Kemudian pada hari terakhir hidupnya, yakni pada Jumat (8/7/2022), Brigadir J juga masih terlibat dalam percakapan di Grup Whatsapp tersebut. |Saat itu pihak keluarga Brigadir J mengirimkan foto keluarga ke grup yang sedang berada di objek wisata pemandian air panas Sipoholon, Tarutung, Sumatera Utara. |Diketahui lokasi tersebut memiliki banyak kenangan bagi Brigadir J lantaran menjadi tempat bermain saat masih kecil.|Brigadir J kemudian menyertakan komentar terhadap foto tersebut. |"Asyik sekali!!!,"katanya. |Kemudian pada pukul 12.58 WIB, keluarga Brigadir J kembali mengirimkan foto ibu ke grup. |Brigadir J membaca pesan tersebut pukul 13.02 WIB, namun tak memberikan tanggapan. |Lalu pada 17.05 WIB menjadi riwayat Whatsapp aktif terakhir kalinya. |Pada pukul 19.34 WIB, ada keluarga yanfg mengirim foto ke grup namun Brigadir J sudah tak membacanya. |Diberitakan sebelumnya, Brigadir J menjadi korban tewas aksi batu tembak sesama polisi di rumah dinas Kadiv Propam, Irjen Pol Ferdy Sambo. |Menurut polisi, baku tembak itu dipicu oleh Brigadir J yang mencoba melakukan tindakan tak senonoh terhadap istri Kadiv Propam, Irjen Ferdy Sambo. |(Tribun-Video.com/TribunJambi.com)|Artikel ini telah tayang title: Alasan Istri Irjen Sambo Minta Perlindungan LPSK
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Pihak lembaga perlindungan saksi dan korban telah menerima surat permohonan perlindungan dari istri Kadiv Propam Polri Irjen Ferdi Sambo.||||Wakil Ketua LPSK Susilaningtias menyebut selanjutnya pihaknya akan melakukan proses investigasi terkait permohonan tersebut.||||Dalam proses investigasi ini LPSK akan berkoordinasi dengan aparat penegak hukum yang menangani laporan perlindungan istri Kadiv Propam Polri.||||Baca Juga Diperiksa Polisi, Istri Kadiv Propam Berikan Kesaksian Dugaan Pelecehan Seksual di https://www.kompas.tv/article/309069/diperiksa-polisi-istri-kadiv-propam-berikan-kesaksian-dugaan-pelecehan-seksual||||"Rabu 13 Juli 2022 sore hari, LPSK menerima permohonan perlindungan dari istri bapak Kadiv propam, yg disampaikan melalui kuasa hukumnya. Selanjutnya LPSK akan melakukan penelahaan dan investigasi terkait dengan permohonan tersebut. Nanti kami akan berkoordinasi dengan aparat penegak hukum yang menangani laporan beliau, kemudian akan menemui beberapa pihak seperti korban sendiri, termasuk keluarga korban dan pihak-pihak lain yang diperlukan,"kata Wakil Ketua LPSK Susilaningtias.||||Setelah itu LPSK juga akan menelaah terkait kebutuhan korban untuk pemulihan trauma, dengan cara melakukan asesmen psikologis.||||Video Editor: Lintang|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/309719/alasan-istri-irjen-sambo-minta-perlindungan-lpsk

title: Watch: Indiana Man Saves Five Kids From Burning Home
description: In Indiana, 25-year-old Nick Bostic is being hailed a hero after leaping into a burning home and saving five people. Authorities say Bostic was driving through Lafayette, Indiana shortly after midnight when he spotted flames, slammed on his breaks and ran into the home. He guided four people outside to safety, then learned that a six-year-old girl was still trapped inside. title: Ayah Brigadir J Yakin Anaknya Tak Masuk Kamar Jika Tak Dipanggil Istri Jenderal
description: JAMBI, KOMPAS.TV  Ayah Brigadir J angkat bicara terkait kronologi versi polisi yang menyebut putranya mencoba masuk ke kamar istri Irjen Ferdi Sambo. ||||Samuel Hutabarat berkeyakinan anaknya tidak akan masuk ke kamar pribadi istri jenderal jika tak dipanggil pemiliknya. ||||"Berhadapan dengan istri seorang jenderal. Dia adalah pengawal kalau gak dipanggil mana mungkin dia datang ke kamar. Menodongkan senjata? Ya tapi terserah, katanya itu kronologisnya. kita sah-sah saja nanti versi orang."ungkap Samuel Hutabarat, pada 13 Juli lalu. ||||Lebih lanjut Samuel juga menjelaskan saat itu situasinya istri Irjen Sambo baru pulang dari luar kota, tidak pulang ke rumah pribadi melainkan rumah dinas. ||||Baca Juga Baju Brigadir J Saat Penembakan Bisa Jadi Petunjuk Kuat, Ini Kata Pakar Hukum di https://www.kompas.tv/article/309443/baju-brigadir-j-saat-penembakan-bisa-jadi-petunjuk-kuat-ini-kata-pakar-hukum||||"Awalnya masuk anak saya ini ke kamar ibu Putri. Saya juga belum pernah ketemu ibu putri. Orang itu baru pulang dari Magelang, anak saya memang ikut, pulang dari luar kota biasa tidak pulang ke rumah pribadi, mereka ke rumah dinas. Sesudah diperiksa, nunggu hasil ibu ini rebahan istirahat di kamar. Di kamar pribadi tak bohong berpakaian. Lalu katanya masuklah anak saya masuk ke kamar."jelas Samuel menirukan penjelasan polisi kepada keluarga. ||||Kini mata publik tertuju pada pengungkapan fakta-fakta di lapangan oleh kepolisian dan tim yang dibentuk. ||||Dalam konferensi pers yang disampaikan Karo Penmas Brigjen Pol Ahmad Ramadhan mengungkap penembakan Brigadir J dimulai ketika teriakan istri Irjen Ferdi Sambo meminta tolong. ||||Brigadir J disebut polisi telah melecehkan istri Irjen Ferdi Sambo dan kemudian ditembak Bharada E yang merupakan penjaga keamanan di rumah itu. ||||Video Editor: Lintang|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/309711/ayah-brigadir-j-yakin-anaknya-tak-masuk-kamar-jika-tak-dipanggil-istri-jenderal

description: A successful first outing for Galtier's men|For the very first match of the 2022-2023 season, Paris Saint-Germain hosted Quevilly-Rouen M√©tropole in a friendly match at the training centre (2-0).|Ten days after the return from holiday for the Red and Blue, the training centre hosted the very first friendly match of the summer this Friday against Quevilly. For his very first match in charge of the Parisians, Christophe Galtier fielded a mixed starting team made up of both young players from the academy and regular starters. The pairing of Messi and Icardi, for example, led the attack alongside Arnaud Kalimuendo, as well as the new recruit Vitinha alongside Paredes in midfield.|Against the Ligue 2 side, the players from the capital showed their intentions from the outset, displaying a desire to impose an intense press. Leo Messi's crosses, Vitinha's silky passes, Juan Bernat's runs down the left flank and Kalimuendo's bursts up front showed the Parisians in good form in the first half and always looking to get on the ball. |Olivier Echouafni's men resisted for a long time, forming a solid block to contain the Parisian attacks. But after a short break to cool off from the intense heat in the French capital, Galtier's players found a new lease of life, which was rewarded by a penalty awarded to Leo Messi and converted by Sergio Ramos (1-0, 33').|The second half of the match saw a complete change of the starting line-up, a new formation and good character from the players, confirming the mood in the squad. title: We Moved, It's Humid, and a Game Changer for Rust Prevention?!
description: The move from Denver to Missouri happened, but not the way I had planned. Thankfully Mom was there to back me up and everything eventually made it to our new home in Missouri. My tools are stuffed in a detached garage and the commercial shop space is still in process. I'll keep you posted as that situation develops.|Since I'm moving from one of the driest cities in the country to one of the more humid cities, I needed to finally take rust prevention seriously. I came across a cool product called Carbon Method and I'm hoping this will be a game-changer for rust prevention. It works by coating the surface with a single layer of graphite, providing a slick surface that's protected from rush for months at a time. Does it work as well as they say? Let's find out together! Check them out at CarbonMethod.com. https://carbonmethod.com/|To reiterate what I said in the video, I purchased this product with my own money. title: Germany's flood catastrophe one year on | DW Documentary
description: The July 2021 flood catastrophe claimed more than 180 lives in Germany alone. The deluge also caused billions of euros‚Äô worth of material damage. Experts warn extreme weather events like this will increase in frequency due to climate change.|It began on the night of 14 July. Heavy rains swept across western Germany. The summer had been wet; the ground was saturated and couldn‚Äôt absorb the water, which flowed into the rivers. Suddenly, even smaller rivers became death traps. The gigantic mass of water devastated entire towns: Bad M√ºnstereifel, Rheinbach, Euskirchen. As the night wore on, the wave surged into the Ahr valley, flooding village after village. Cars and trees, bridges and houses were swept away.|People sought refuge on rooftops, where many had to wait all night to be rescued by helicopter. But some couldn‚Äôt be saved. They were either carried off by the floodwater or taken by surprise in cellars or underground parking lots. More than 180 people died. Thousands of residents lost everything. It was the worst natural disaster in Germany for almost 60 years.|But what followed restored hope. Volunteers traveled to the flood-hit areas from all over Germany. They dug mud out of the houses, removed the debris and also took the time to talk to those affected. Many farmers arrived in tractors to help clear the roads. Donations hit record levels.|Lothar Schr√∂der‚Äôs film charts the course of events, highlighting the suffering of those affected and the indomitable spirit of those who pitched in to help in the aftermath. description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Sudah sepekan kasus tewasnya polisi di rumah jenderal ini bergulir, publik masih menanti apa titik terang dari kasus ini.||||Kapolri pun kembali menyatakan akan mengusut kasus ini secara transparan.||||Untuk sekian kalinya, Kapolri menengaskan berkomitmen menyelesaikan kasus penembakan, Brigadir J secara subjektif dan transparan. ||||Hal ini kembali disampaikan, melalui Kabagpenum Polri, Kombes Nurul Azizah.||||Baca Juga Istri Ketua RT Lingkungan Rumah Kadiv Propam Buka Alasan sang Suami Belum Bisa Ditemui Wartawan Lagi di https://www.kompas.tv/article/309536/istri-ketua-rt-lingkungan-rumah-kadiv-propam-buka-alasan-sang-suami-belum-bisa-ditemui-wartawan-lagi||||Olah TKP pun kembali dilakukan hari ini.||||Ini adalah kali keempat polisi melakukan olah TKP di kediaman Irjen Ferdy Sambo, Duren Tiga Jakarta Selatan.||||Sudah satu pekan kasus ini bergulir dan terang kasus ini pun masih jadi pertanyaan utamanya oleh pihak keluarga Brigadir J.||||Pakar Hukum Universitas Jambi menyatakan baju yang di pakai korban saat kejadian bisa menjadi barang bukti yang kuat dan petunjuk penyebab kematian, dari baju tersebut bisa di lihat apakah robek dengan senjata tajam atau dengan tembakan.||||Kasus ini  bisa diungkap asal penyelidikannya di serahkan ke Mabes Polri.|||| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/309560/lakukan-olah-tkp-untuk-keempat-kalinya-tim-khusus-kapolri-siap-ungkap-kasus-kematian-brigadir-j

title: Presidential race: Droupadi Murmu gets opposition support; After JMM, now Akhilesh ally backs
description: Yashwant Sinha is losing more opposition votes in the race for the Presidential post. After Congress ally JMM's, Hemant Soren declared support for NDA'a Droupadi Murmu, Samajwadi Party's ally, Suheldev Bhartiya Samaj Party, has pledged support to Murmu. The Presidential elections will take place on July 18.
